      "column": "left",
      "text": "Deew8 irr mannu8 Eenatdnee- \ntam Deewa Schkirstam Weetu/ \nkus zaur mannu Rohku faploh- \nun uszehle tam weenu Telti. \nstjs/ itt ka Uhdens isplohsahs. \nTadehf nofanze tee to Weetu \nBaal-Brazim.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 12,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un tee pamette tur fa- \nwne Deewus/ tad pawehleja \nDahwids/ ka tohs bij ar uggu- \nnt fadedsinaht.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 13,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Bet tee Wilisteri bandi- \njahs atkat/un apmettahs Geletja.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 14,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tad waizaja Dahwids \natkat Deewu/ un Deews fazzi- \nja us to: Tew ne buhs ns aug- \nschu eet winneem pakkat/ eij ap- \nfahrt no augsch puffes prett win- \nxeem/ un nahz pee teem prett \nteem Randa-Rohkeem.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 15,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un kad tu Trohfsni dsir- \ndesi Randa-Rohkn Wirs Gallds/ \ntad iseij us Kautchann/jo Deews \nbuhs tawa Preefscha tsgahjis \nto Wilisteru Lehgeri kant.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 16,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un Dahwids darrija ta/ \nka Deew8 tam bij pawehlejs/ \nun tee kawe to Wilisteru Lehge- \nri/ no Gibeona lihds Gaseraf.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 17,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Ta ispanda Dahwida \nSlava wifas Semmes Mal- \nlas/ un tas KUNGS mette \nwinnu Bihjaschanu pahr wif- \njeem Pagazzeem.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tad fazziia Dahwids: Ne \nweens warr to Deewa Schkirstu \nnest/ ka ween tee Lewiti/ jo tohs \nirr tas KUNGS iswehlejs/ ka \nteem buhs to Deewa Schkirstu \nnest/ un winnam kalpoht nuh- \nschigt.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 2,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Pehz sapulzeja Dahwids \nwiffu Israelu uhs Jerusalemi/ \nka tee to Deewa Schkirstu us \naugschu sawa Weeta westu/ ko \nwinsch tam bij tataifsjs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 3,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un Dahwids fasanze Aa- \nrona Behrnus/ un tohs Lewitus.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 4,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "No Kaata Behrneem bija/ \nUriels tas Wirfneeks ar faweem \nBrahkeem/ fimts un diwidef- \nmits.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 5,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "No Meraza Behrneem/ \nAsajus tas Wirfneeks ar fatweem \nBrahkeem/ diwisints un divi- \ndefmits.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 6,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "No Gersona Behrneem/ \nJoels tas Wirfneeks ar faweem \nBrahkeem/ fimts un trihsdef- \nmits.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 7,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "No Elizawana Behrneem/ \nSema jus tas Wirfneeks ar fa- \nweem Brahkeem/ diwisints.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 8,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "No Eebroza Behrneem/ \nEstels tas Wirfneeks ar faweem \nBrahkeem/ astondefmits.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 9,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "No Usicfa Behrneem/ \nAmminadabs tas Wirfneeks ar \nfaweem Brahkeem/ fimts un di- \nwipadefmits.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 10,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un Dahwids afzinaja \ntohs Preesterus Zadaku un Ab- \njataru/\n"
    }
  ],
